# Local environment
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Docker / runtime state — never commit. The negations below exempt
# the in-tree ``src/alfred/state/`` Python package (ADR-0018 — typed
# state.git proposal payloads), the matching
# ``tests/integration/state/`` round-trip suite, the
# ``tests/unit/state/`` model-validator regression suite, and the
# ``tests/adversarial/state/`` replay-safety suite (ADR-0021 #171);
# the runtime state.git store at ``/var/lib/alfred/state.git`` and any
# developer-mounted ``./state/`` bind volume still match.
state/
!src/alfred/state/
!src/alfred/state/**
!tests/integration/state/
!tests/integration/state/**
!tests/unit/state/
!tests/unit/state/**
!tests/adversarial/state/
!tests/adversarial/state/**
# Re-mask Python build artifacts that the un-negation above re-exposed.
# CR-rework round-2 MINOR T7: the un-ignore ``tests/adversarial/state/**``
# can re-include nested ``__pycache__`` directories at arbitrary depth;
# the top-level ``__pycache__/`` ignore matches only the basename so a
# nested ``tests/adversarial/state/subdir/__pycache__/`` slips back in.
# The explicit recursive re-ignores below close every depth.
tests/unit/state/__pycache__/
tests/unit/state/**/__pycache__/
tests/integration/state/__pycache__/
tests/integration/state/**/__pycache__/
tests/adversarial/state/__pycache__/
tests/adversarial/state/**/__pycache__/
src/alfred/state/__pycache__/
src/alfred/state/**/__pycache__/
data/
*.db
*.sqlite*

