WARP.md

# Secrets — never commit; see ADR-0012. The file-backed SecretBroker reads
# from ~/.config/alfred/secrets.toml (host) or /etc/alfred/secrets.toml
# (container); test fixtures that synthesise the production filename are
# caught by the third `**` pattern even when nested under tests/.
secrets.toml
secrets.*.toml
**/secrets.toml
